metadata.name: OxygenFreeNFT
metadata.description: We are here as the first NFT project that can be implemented in the world. One tree will be planted for every nft you buy. You will view it on our site with its coordinates and pictures. As our project develops, the dry areas decided by the community will be greened, the lands will be purchased and progress will be made with the community. It's time to green the world. Breathe !!
